projects.name: Dijkstras Algorithm
projects.description: Dijkstra's Algorithm- is a solution to the single source shortest path problem in graph theory. Dijkstra's original algorithm found the shortest path between two given nodes, but a more common variant fixes a single node as the 'source' node and finds shortest paths from the source to all other nodes in the graph, producing a shortest- path.
